{"tid":908603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬爾代夫將退出中國自由貿易協議","createTime":"2018-11-19T16:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T02:25:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d64b0c3680f6bc9445143d3a5c124ff1bc4f56","tid":908603,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"馬爾代夫民主黨領導人納希德(Mohamed Nasheed)稱，馬爾代夫新政府將退出與中國的自由貿易協議(FTA)，因為像馬爾代夫這樣一個小國與中國達成這種協議是個錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n路透引述納希德稱，中國和馬爾代夫的貿易失衡如此嚴重，沒人會考慮雙方在這種情形下簽訂自由貿易協議，中國從不由馬爾代夫購買任何東西，這是一個單向條約。<br />\n<br />\n納希德是馬爾代夫前總統，目前是新任總統薩利赫的顧問。納希德指出，議會不會通過零關稅協議生效所需的法律變更。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1995867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1995867&d=Kw%2FU6yUwWLd772NRwAvJUTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=38476c0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1995867</a>"},{"pid":"39e0abf1c80eaacd546f2035684845fbcf39bdc7","tid":908603,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"27291a46f7afcdb9f16a57b6d348ad4e8e1118bd","tid":908603,"uid":13663,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/194758_b86c66365af6294f88162f6d1d61c0c7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F194758_b86c66365af6294f88162f6d1d61c0c7.gif&h=a6d6d3cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"507a0340e7cfc5e33e90d88ce2140565747d76d7","tid":908603,"uid":22913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"希望支那罷去馬爾代夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067274f237b9ec52fc3716f62ab4dca0ea7f5c45","tid":908603,"uid":4964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"中國人又罷去馬爾代夫,正<br />\n宣佈變歷史文件就啱架啦"},{"pid":"2abb5f9bd1ef834454326110b5de6c185f47e403","tid":908603,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:39:52.000Z","msg":"早兩日先講完，今日嚟料"},{"pid":"ba10189b3ab3dc3d400152332285e18225d049f3","tid":908603,"uid":64922,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:40:43.000Z","msg":"支那口交部1日24個鐘前重話務實合作，推進「一帶一路」建設，24個鐘依家馬爾代夫就同你反檯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雒樹剛表示，中方重視中馬關係，願同馬爾代夫共同努力，鞏固傳統友誼，加強發展戰略對接，規劃好雙邊務實合作，推進「一帶一路」建設，為中馬面向未來的全面友好合作夥伴關係注入新動力。<br />\n<br />\n薩利赫感謝習近平主席派特使出席其就職典禮，讚賞中方長期以來對馬發展提供的支持和幫助。薩利赫表示，馬新政府重視並致力於發展對華關係，堅定奉行一個中國政策，願加強兩國高層交往，進一步深化雙方在「一帶一路」框架下的務實合作，不斷豐富兩國關係內涵。<br />\n<br />\n應馬爾代夫政府邀請，習近平主席特使、文化和旅遊部部長雒樹剛於上周六（17日）在馬爾代夫首都馬累出席薩利赫總統的就職典禮。"},{"pid":"8e7c8a6eb9099f7e950f56d3a832c41a3673bf92","tid":908603,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"067274f237b9ec52fc3716f62ab4dca0ea7f5c45","tid":908603,"uid":4964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"中國人又罷去馬爾代夫,正<br />\n宣佈變歷史文件就啱架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"直頭鎖國啦屌"},{"pid":"f86afba546cc48ce40eae26f3cc0b17d8835a918","tid":908603,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"爭落啲債唔洗還<br />\nhappy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a708d1d57db9f802d3e73ecf56329b794cd4d4e","tid":908603,"uid":92178,"